    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Success
---
The grand secret of humanity is its inability to perceive its own spiritual
character. Mankind is nothing less than miniature gods in the unfolding.
When the ancient masters bid their students “To know thyself,” they were
merely guiding them to this sacred knowledge.
